parameters: Are you practicing in a place like this again?
Coleus, if you don't like it, then fight back

Honestly... is he kind or just foolish?

The items for confession at the store are now available for purchase.
Well, but having fought me 200 times, your moves aren't bad at all.
Thanks for always practicing with me
Eh... It's not a big deal, it's good practice for me too...
I usually finish them off in an instant, but
A-anyway, I'll always be your practice partner.
You don't need to hold back at all, okay?
It has been my lifelong goal to become a knight.
I have to leave this place.
So, it's time to say goodbye to Coleus..
I'll become strong and come to see you someday
But Coleus is weak, isn't he?

It's good to practice here together, isn't it?
This is where I first met Coleus, too...
Why did you suddenly call for Coleus?
I like you, will you go out with me?
(Do I have the right to date Coleus after sleeping with another man?)
Yes, please take care of me.
It seems like Artel is looking at Coleus's face with some kind of expectation.

It felt strange to kiss Artel, whom I had spent time with since we were little,
like this.

It's my first kiss, so I may not do it well, but I moved my lips as I
pleased.
It felt like Artel was a little more accustomed to kissing in comparison.
There's something I need to talk to you about...
There's a \C[2]lust mark\C[0] engraved on my body...

I don't have that kind of thing... just...
My body easily gets aroused and becomes sensitive...
When I was pursuing the enemy alone during a mission...
I was ensnared and branded with a lewd mark
(It's more calming to be alone, but..)
(This way, it won't be a good practice..)

Sorry, can I use this place?
Well then, I'll be heading home.
But, I just got blown away..
Thank you, please ask me again next time
(Even though I used to scare people..)
